{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/animate-elements-continually-using-an-infinite-animation-count","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Animirajte elemente neprekidno koristeći beskonačan broj animacija","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Prethodni izazovi su pokrili kako koristiti neka svojstva animacije i <code>@keyframes</code> pravilo. Drugo svojstvo animacije je <code>animation-iteration-count</code>, koje vam omogućava da kontrolišete koliko puta želite da ponovite animaciju. Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">animation-iteration-count: 3;\n</code></pre>\n<p>U ovom slučaju animacija će se zaustaviti nakon što se pokrene 3 puta, ali je moguće učiniti da se animacija nastavi zauvek postavljanjem te vrednosti na <code>infinite</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78a8367417b2b2512ae3","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Da bi lopta nastavila da skače udesno u beskonačnom ciklusu, promenite <code>animation-iteration-count</code> svojstvo na <code>infinite</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cVJDVfq","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301041,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/animate-elements-continually-using-an-infinite-animation-count"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n\n  #ball {\n    width: 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n    margin: 50px auto;\n    position: relative;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: linear-gradient(\n      35deg,\n      #ccffff,\n      #ffcccc\n    );\n    animation-name: bounce;\n    animation-duration: 1s;\n    animation-iteration-count: 3;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes bounce{\n    0% {\n      top: 0px;\n    }\n    50% {\n      top: 249px;\n      width: 130px;\n      height: 70px;\n    }\n    100% {\n      top: 0px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<div id=\"ball\"></div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>animation-iteration-count</code> svojstvo treba da ima vrednost <code>infinite</code>.</p>","testString":"const ballElement = document.querySelector('#ball');\nconst ballStyle = window.getComputedStyle(ballElement); \nassert.equal(ballStyle?.animationIterationCount, 'infinite');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"animate-elements-continually-using-an-infinite-animation-count","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/make-a-css-heartbeat-using-an-infinite-animation-count","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-visual-direction-by-fading-an-element-from-left-to-right","id":"587d78a8367417b2b2512ae3","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n  